OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FA man who stabbed a father-of-three to
OL,7,Fdeath in a "revenge" attack after a
OL,8,Ffight in a pub has been jailed for
OL,9,Flife.
OL,11,FBrandon Byrne, 23, chased 40-year-old
OL,12,FJames Cook down the street and stabbed
OL,13,Fhim twice, as well as kicking him as
OL,14,Fhe lay injured, after they were
OL,15,Fejected from the pub in Newark.
OL,17,FMr Cook was described by his widow as
OL,18,F"the greatest dad" as Byrne was jailed
OL,19,Ffor a minimum term of 23 years.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
