FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777655153
OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FSentencing Byrne, Judge Steven
OL,7,FCoupland told him: "In an incident
OL,8,Flasting less than two minutes just
OL,9,Fbefore midnight a year ago yesterday
OL,10,Fyou murdered James Cook.
OL,12,F"I am satisfied you had become angry
OL,13,Fand you were looking for revenge."
OL,15,FNottingham Crown Court heard Byrne and
OL,16,FMr Cook had been involved in a fight
OL,17,Fon 30 April last year after words were
OL,18,Fexchanged between their friendship
OL,19,Fgroups.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777655153
OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FByrne was headbutted and suffered a
OL,7,Fbite injury to his lip during the
OL,8,Fbrawl, before both men were told to
OL,9,Fleave.
OL,11,FByrne was seen on CCTV pulling out a
OL,12,Fknife before chasing Mr Cook and
OL,13,Fattacking him in Castle Gate.
OL,15,FPart-way through the fatal attack
OL,16,FByrne "paused" and kicked the victim
OL,17,Fto the head, the court heard.
OL,26,@xD@GOUxD@NO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777655153
OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FJudge Coupland said the second stab
OL,7,Fwound was inflicted while Mr Cook was
OL,8,Fdefenceless on the ground. He died a
OL,9,Fshort time later.
OL,11,FBody-worn video showed Byrne, formerly
OL,12,Fof Winston Court, Newark, asking
OL,13,Fofficers "did he die?" when he was
OL,14,Farrested.
OL,16,FByrne, dressed in a blue suit and a
OL,17,Fred tie for his sentencing hearing,
OL,18,Fwas found guilty of murder on
OL,19,FThursday, the first anniversary of the
OL,20,Fkilling.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
