FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777655153
OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FHe showed no emotion during victim
OL,7,Fimpact statements describing him as a
OL,8,F"monster" who had cruelly "destroyed
OL,9,Fan entire family".
OL,11,FIn a statement, Mr Cook's widow Adele
OL,12,Fsaid: "James was the greatest dad and
OL,13,Fthe greatest love of my life.
OL,15,F"He was my partner, my protector and
OL,16,Fmy best friend. To my children, he was
OL,17,Ftheir hero."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]pD@[OUqD@QO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777655153
OL,3,CMan who stabbed 'greatest dad' after
OL,4,Cpub brawl jailed for murder
OL,6,FDet Con Kimberley Priestley, of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "It's
OL,8,Fbeen almost a year to the day since
OL,9,FBrandon Byrne turned the lives of
OL,10,FJames Cook's family upside down.
OL,12,F"They've been put through hell since
OL,13,Fhe produced a knife and callously
OL,14,Fmurdered their loved one with it that
OL,15,Fnight on 30 April last year."
OL,17,FShe added: "While the outcome of this
OL,18,Ftrial and the sentencing that has now
OL,19,Fbeen passed will never bring Mr Cook
OL,20,Fback, our hope is that it will help
OL,21,Fhis family as they continue to grieve."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
